reviewText: Exact same episode as Season 1 Episode 2.
I thought this episode was great, didn't seem that the quality was that good though. I had to switch browsers twice because it crashed on me. Could be Amazon problem, could be my computer/

Some of the episodes are very boring. It's still educational and worth watching, just nothing 'wowed' me but that's just a personal opinion. Experiences may differ. In case anyone was wondering it includes episodes such as 'Sacred Pain,' 'Marks of Identity,' and 'Delicacies.'

I really only watched this show while I was doing other things because it just wasn't that interesti g,  Unfortunately I cannot really give an intelligent review because I didn't pay it that much attention.
this season was just as good as the first.its a good gift for anyone who loves national geographics or wierd things!
